milestones.description: Norman Vanua and Chad Soper's 14-run partnership is PNG's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 7 between Willie Gavera and Chad Soper
Chad Soper has become the top wicket-taker for PNG in ODIs with 9 wickets, going past Mahuru Dai's 6
This is the lowest match aggregate (388) involving teams Hong Kong & P.N.G. in ODIs
Norman Vanua has broken the record for most ducks (1) in ODIs for PNG, going past Charles Amini's 1
Mahuru Dai has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (4) for PNG, going past Willie Gavera
